{"tid":1079364,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"發現用牛油果醬代替柱侯醬黎炆牛腩都唔錯","createTime":"2019-03-27T01:49:10.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-27T08:09:19.000Z","uid":171273,"like":14,"dislike":82,"uniUserReply":38,"replies":[{"pid":"65c4d6fb47b99d240268d9a872cd5a592a6bf277","tid":1079364,"uid":171273,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-27T01:49:10.000Z","msg":"早幾日同女朋友去中環某間墨西哥餐廳食完nachos<br />\n<br />\n發現用黎點nachos果D牛油果醬好撚滑嫩又好香<br />\n<br />\n於是返屋企自己整左兜<br />\n<br />\n我既牛油果醬做法係將4個牛油果去皮然後放入搞拌機 落兩粒蒜頭同4分1個橙攪勻(屋企無檸檬所以用左橙黎代替)<br />\n<br />\n然後買左包dorito黎點 發現仲有唔少剩<br />\n<br />\n於是拎左黎炆牛腩<br />\n<br />\n牛腩我揀左本地既坑腩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n然後因為我唔鍾意食白蘿蔔 於是用左薯仔代替<br />\n<br />\n做法主要都係參考鼎爺做法 youtube搵到 我唔幫TVB賺click了<br />\n<br />\n咩草果八角唔記得買 用左屋企整蛋糕有剩既丁香同玉桂代替<br />\n<br />\n然後將柱侯醬換哂做牛油果醬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n出黎個樣有d似pesto既意粉 味道絕對唔差過港島某出名牛腩店<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d7a6ca63ec2ba0f72acdb550b7933e1b66e043a9","tid":1079364,"uid":171273,"like":4,"dislike":21,"score":-17,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-27T01:50:28.000Z","msg":"牛油果果種油香味 同牛腩既肉味配合得天衣無縫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n用dorito再點牛腩個醬 仲正過用麵包點紅湯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n食左兩碗飯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"69d09e7a39370d47487fc31c43f36470900c48c0","tid":1079364,"uid":171273,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-27T01:54:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"994ab299961dae32c5328bf4f6cba348d32ef109","tid":1079364,"uid":9053,"like":58,"dislike":0,"score":58,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-27T01:55:30.000Z","msg":"睇字已經想嘔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />　咪撚貼圖唔該<i